with a power accounting that

00:02:28.820 --> 00:02:31.580
would take into account systems
where the scattering length is

00:02:31.580 --> 00:02:34.260
large, or in particular,
the scattering length times

00:02:34.260 --> 00:02:37.640
momentum is greater than 1, and
in these two-nucleon systems

00:02:37.640 --> 00:02:40.380
